{
  "stem": "2980.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We also opened up a-- we built a new store, which we never occupied, because the war broke out, which was supposed to be for agricultural equipment, radios, and bicycles, in the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a-- a natural inventor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He worked in this shop, machine shop, with his brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had three brothers and a sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she would be a secretary sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His oldest brother was Gershon, then was Zelig, and Mershel, and Iossel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had four brothers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would work with him in-- in the machine shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father, I was told that he was a-- he was a quiet man, but he was a genius.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time we didn't have electricity, so he made a battery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had electricity from the battery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then he-- we didn't-- he didn't want to-- when electricity came in sometime in the '20s, he made an invention where the-- where the light would be connected to a certain central switch.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that switch would be connected to a wire down to where my-- my mother would light the candles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And with a thread, he would put a candle on top of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When the candle burned out, which means around 11:00, 11:30 at night, the candle would light the wire, and the weight would pull the-- the wire, the whole thing, it would shut off the switch.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then he improved on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he made a-- he connected it with a grandfather clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he could pinpoint to the minute when he wanted the electricity to go off before Shabbos, because he was orthodox.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He at one time, he also made scale that you weigh tons.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
